SUMMARY:ZYDECO FLAMES
DESCRIPTION:DINNER SHOW with ZYDECO FLAMES\nThe Zydeco Flames have gained a reputation as the West Coast’s premiere Zydeco band. The Flames consistently pack the house in venues ranging from contemporary clubs to major festivals and traditional dance halls. Their sizzling roots rhythms are timeless and the execution of them relentless\, with a stunningly powerful groove.
