SUMMARY:JERRY HANNAN & CHRIS MURPHY
DESCRIPTION:JERRY HANNAN\, A Marin County Treasure + CHRIS MURPHY\nA distinguished songwriter and entertainer\, Jerry Hannan recorded his own song\, “Society” with Pearl Jam’s Eddie Vedder\, which is featured in Sean Penn’s film Into the Wild.  “I Thought I Was You”\, written by Jerry and brother Sean Hannan also plays in Into the Wild.
URL:https://ranchonicasio.com/event/jerry-hannan-chris-murphy-3/
LOCATION:Rancho Nicasio\, 1 Old Rancheria Rd\, Nicasio\, CA\, 94946\, United States
