SUMMARY:IKO YAYA
DESCRIPTION:IKO YAYA \nPronounced I – KO – YAH-YAH. Since 2013\, Iko YaYa has been playing the Louisiana-influenced music that gets folks on their the feet – what they like to call “swamp ‘n roll!” \nThe band: Jim Scott – guitar\, Cheryl McBride – vocals & percussion\, Sam Siggins – drums & vocals\, Lance Houck – bass & vocals\, Andre Nigoghossian – accordion & vocals\, Susan Copperman – saxophone
