SUMMARY:JOHNNY & JUNE FOREVER
DESCRIPTION:Dinner Show with JOHNNY & JUNE FOREVER\nJohnny Cash and June Carter were well known performers before meeting\, and like their predecessors\, Danny Evans and Essence of ‘Johnny & June Forever’ are also seasoned artists in their own rights. Their chemistry and musicality on stage is so undeniable that many have described them as the reincarnation of Johnny & June.
