SUMMARY:FEELING GROOVY - Rancho Debut!
DESCRIPTION:FEELING GROOVY – Rancho Debut!\nWith a deep respect for the duo’s timeless music\, Feeling Groovy reimagines the magic of Paul Simon and Art Garfunkel’s collaboration that once dominated the folk scene. Through a blend of powerful vocals\, intricate harmonies\, and engaging storytelling\, the band recreates the magic of their live performances\, transporting audiences back to the heyday of one of the most beloved acts in music history.
URL:https://ranchonicasio.com/event/feeling-groovy-rancho-debut/
LOCATION:Rancho Nicasio\, 1 Old Rancheria Rd\, Nicasio\, CA\, 94946\, United States
