SUMMARY:MARSHALL HOUSE PROJECT- Rancho Debut!
DESCRIPTION:MARSHALL HOUSE PROJECT- Rancho Debut! \nMarshall House Project (Voted 2025’s Best Funk Band of the North Bay by The Bohemian) is a driving soul funk outfit with one foot rooted deep in the pockets of the past and the other fearlessly exploring the deep fry of the future. The sound is an eclectic electric love child: the product of an affair between Jimi Hendrix and The Funky Meters\, after a long night of drinking with space aliens and jamming to Bob on the jukebox. MHP delivers a volcanic performance of energetic funk and slinky soul with a psychedelic twist and a chili salt rim. The mission: to create an uplifting dance experience spun full of twists and turns\, interlaced with conscious reflective lyrics and sizzling solos expanding\, contracting and alive\, like a universe unto itself. \n 
URL:https://ranchonicasio.com/event/marshall-house-project-rancho-debut/
LOCATION:Rancho Nicasio\, 1 Old Rancheria Rd\, Nicasio\, CA\, 94946\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://ranchonicasio.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/MHP-orange-w-logo-resized.png
END:VEVENT
