SUMMARY:THE HOT LICKS- celebrating the music of Dan Hicks
DESCRIPTION:DINNER SHOW with THE HOT LICKS- celebrating the music of Dan Hicks\nThe Hot Licks\, original members of Dan’s backing band\, perform Dan’s classic songs in the style that Dan Hicks invented – Folk/Swing! – A blend of Gypsy Jazz\, Folk and Swing with lots of vocal harmonies. The Hot Licks are dedicated to preserving the original sound and spirit in the way Dan taught them! They carry the torch for Folk-Swing with his signature style that has inspired so many others. “The group’s hallmark country/jazz styled vocals shined\, highlighted by delectable guitar and violin solos.\nThe spirit and the sound of that previous Incarnation with Dan Hicks and his spirit is imbued in their sound. A rare occasion not to be missed!” – Arne Frager\, The Plant Studios
URL:https://ranchonicasio.com/event/the-hot-licks-celebrating-the-music-of-dan-hicks-2/
LOCATION:Rancho Nicasio\, 1 Old Rancheria Rd\, Nicasio\, CA\, 94946\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://ranchonicasio.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/570146-1.png
END:VEVENT
